<paragraph blockId="10.[189,1399,891,988]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Antenna black but postpedicel contrastingly reddish yellow. All tibiae yellow. Hind tibiae lacking long black dorsal bristles, but long fine yellowish hairs present; ventrally with long fine black bristles twice as long as width of tibia.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
