<paragraph blockId="13.[189,1398,1452,1555]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
For the identification of the Afrotropical 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bigot" authorityYear="1857" box="[693,853,1452,1478]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Crossopalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[693,853,1452,1478]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Crossopalpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
we refer to the keys of 
<bibRefCitation author="Raffone G." box="[1161,1344,1452,1478]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="219 - 229" refId="ref6615" refString="Raffone G. 1994. Terzo contributo alla conoscenza dei ditteri Hybotidi della Sierra Leone. Accademia nazionale dei Lincei 267: 219 - 229." type="journal article" year="1994">Raffone (1994)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Grootaert P. &amp; Shamshev I." box="[189,551,1490,1516]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="1 - 61" refId="ref6494" refString="Grootaert P. &amp; Shamshev I. 2012. The flies of the family Hybotidae (Diptera, Empidoidea) collected during the Boyekoli Ebale Congo 2010 Expedition in Democratic Republic of Congo. Zootaxa 3603: 1 - 61. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3603.1" type="journal article" year="2012">Grootaert &amp; Shamshev (2012)</bibRefCitation>
. Illustrations of the various lobes of the right surstylus of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wiedemann" authorityYear="1830" box="[1279,1398,1491,1516]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Crossopalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aenescens">
<emphasis box="[1279,1398,1491,1516]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">aenescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group can be found in 
<bibRefCitation author="Smith K. G. V." box="[454,613,1528,1555]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="1 - 16" refId="ref6677" refString="Smith K. G. V. 1967. Afrikanische Empididae (Dipt.). Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A 179: 1 - 16." type="journal article" year="1967">Smith (1967)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
